{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then we didn't get any more paid, so we had our nine-- three days, because we had our nine mark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then they opened a shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And in that shop you could buy two things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You could buy either an envelope, a sheet of paper, and borrow a pencil to write to Auschwitz to your family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Which, of course, was absolutely ridiculous, but many people did it because they didn't believe that their people weren't in Auschwitz anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Or you could buy a lipstick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I don't remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I know that I didn't buy the lipstick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I think I did buy a paper so as to have paper, a sheet of paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I didn't send it off because there was no point of sending it off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But I did buy-- I didn't buy lipstick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The women went mad and were killing each other for the lipstick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There weren't enough lipsticks to go around, and they weren't the right colors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So if anybody found the right colors, they were killing each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Now, at that time to me it was completely ludicrous, and the German's were laughing their heads off about the stupid women who are starving, who look emaciated, who look terrible, who are in clothes which don't fit them, and yet they-- they kill each other for a lipstick.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I didn't understand it, but today I think I understand it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They had to somehow-- I was never vain, so I couldn't have understood at the time at all, because I didn't use a lipstick.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I refused to use lipstick or powder or anything because I always said I must be loved for myself, not how I make myself up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I mustn't put on a mask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But-- but today I understand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
